pkgfilecache Changes
=====================

Version 0.1.4
-------------
- Disable all unit tests that require downloaded data on CRAN
- Use the same name for the vignette title and the vignette index entry
Note: This release contains no feature changes for package users, it was required for technical reasons related to CRAN.


Version 0.1.3
-------------
- Delete test data after tests on CRAN
Note: This release contains no feature changes for package users, it was required for technical reasons related to CRAN.


Version 0.1.2
--------------
- Fix bug in accessing files in local sub directories of the package cache
- Document how to download files to a local subdir in the vignette
- Document how to access files in local subdir in the vignette
- Adapt tests to make package build for MacOS on CRAN


Version 0.1.1
--------------
- Added support for storing files in sub directories in the local file cache


Version 0.1.0
--------------
- Initial release
